      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "Create a compelling 10-episode story arc now. Generate it fully.",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a master storyteller. You must generate ALL output strictly in Azerbaijani language.\n\nCreate a serialized story about ONE unnamed man who lives in a house with a yard. Over 10 episodes, he secretly builds something extraordinary underground — a secret basement, bunker, underground room, hidden library, or any fascinating underground space. Each episode should:\n\n- Show real physical progress (digging, building, installing, decorating)\n- Include one surprising discovery or challenge per episode\n- Feel cinematic and viral-worthy\n- Build suspense — neighbors/family almost discover it\n- End with a cliffhanger or reveal that makes you want to watch the next episode\n\nThe story must have:\n- A consistent main character (never named)\n- A consistent location (suburban house with yard)\n- A clear goal that is revealed gradually\n- Emotional depth — why is he building this?\n\nOutput ONLY a JSON object:\n{\n  \"story_title\": \"Short viral title in Azerbaijani\",\n  \"story_summary\": \"2-3 sentence summary in Azerbaijani\",\n  \"underground_place\": \"What he is building (e.g. secret library, bunker, underground greenhouse)\",\n  \"character_motivation\": \"Why he is building it (1 sentence)\"\n}"
        }
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 1.9,
      "position": [
        608,
        1296
      ],
