        "text": "=Based on this story arc, create exactly 10 episodes:\n\nStory Title: {{ $json.output.story_title }}\nSummary: {{ $json.output.story_summary }}\nUnderground place: {{ $json.output.underground_place }}\nMotivation: {{ $json.output.character_motivation }}\n\nGenerate all 10 episodes now.",
